You are all Sahaja Yogis,

00:01:07.542 --> 00:01:12.291
and there should not be
controversy between you.

00:01:14.875 --> 00:01:20.417
You should all think of
the same thing, isn't it?

00:01:22.583 --> 00:01:26.417
I feel sorry so many
standing outside.

