Can you move
the piano behind?

00:01:42.125 --> 00:01:44.500
You are from Como?

00:01:44.999 --> 00:01:47.333
See! He could come!

00:02:10.458 --> 00:02:13.542
I'm happy to see all of you here.

00:02:16.917 --> 00:02:18.875
May God bless you.

00:02:21.500 --> 00:02:23.208
You are so many.

00:02:23.458 --> 00:02:26.834
And you can afford to have a hall,

00:02:27.250 --> 00:02:29.333
all of you sitting there,

00:02:29.625 --> 00:02:32.999
and I feeling comfortable.

00:02:38.125 --> 00:02:41.500
After all, you are
all Sahaja Yogis,

00:02:41.667 --> 00:02:44.542
all brothers and sisters.

00:02:47.208 --> 00:02:51.959
and you don't mind
any inconvenience,

00:02:52.291 --> 00:02:55.333
but if we can make
something convenient,

00:02:55.583 --> 00:02:57.583
we should do it.

00:03:06.166 --> 00:03:11.583
No,no, I have no trouble, I have
come all the way from India!

00:03:22.917 --> 00:03:26.125
For My convenience you

00:03:26.709 --> 00:03:29.125
take no such a note.

00:03:30.458 --> 00:03:34.166
See, wherever you are, wherever
you have the programme,

00:03:34.333 --> 00:03:36.709
I'll go there.

00:03:36.917 --> 00:03:40.834
As long as possible
I will definitely go.

00:03:53.750 --> 00:03:58.375
These days, life is much
more comfortable

00:03:58.792 --> 00:04:01.542
but when I was working
in the villages.

00:04:01.750 --> 00:04:04.500
I used to go on
the bullock cart.

00:04:05.250 --> 00:04:08.583
You've got photograph,
you can see

00:04:09.500 --> 00:04:13.792
- on the bullock cart to go
for miles together.

00:04:15.917 --> 00:04:18.250
I knew I had to
do all that.

00:04:18.458 --> 00:04:23.125
If I have to get Sahaja Yogis,
I have to work that way.

00:04:24.542 --> 00:04:26.959
And I was
quite prepared.

00:04:28.542 --> 00:04:30.709
I never felt any
exhaustion

00:04:31.667 --> 00:04:34.500
with it, never.

00:04:35.333 --> 00:04:39.917
On the contrary, after I meet
you all I feel so happy.

00:04:46.917 --> 00:04:50.375
Now, is there somebody
who has problems?

00:04:58.500 --> 00:05:02.542
Anybody -  who
has problems...

00:05:03.583 --> 00:05:05.875
Alcohol, drinking,
alcohol.

00:05:07.959 --> 00:05:11.125
They are not in
Sahaja Yoga? - No.

00:05:12.000 --> 00:05:16.166
Why not? You are
the mother?

00:05:18.333 --> 00:05:19.458
Yes...and
my husband.

00:05:19.792 --> 00:05:21.542
How about
the children?

00:05:22.250 --> 00:05:23.750
I have two
children with him.

00:05:25.375 --> 00:05:26.999
The children are...are they
Sahaja Yogis your children?

00:05:27.041 --> 00:05:29.125
Not, the two older
children not.

00:05:29.333 --> 00:05:31.750
How many children
you have? - Four.

00:05:30.999 --> 00:05:33.291
Four children,
four children

00:05:34.458 --> 00:05:35.709
They are not
Sahaja Yogis?

00:05:37.542 --> 00:05:39.583
Only my two
young ones.

00:05:40.375 --> 00:05:44.166
Two young children in Sahaja Yoga and the
two older ones are not in Sahaja Yoga,

00:05:44.458 --> 00:05:46.542
husband is not
in Sahaja Yoga.

00:05:48.375 --> 00:05:50.041
Surprising.

00:05:56.250 --> 00:06:02.166
But here the family system is
good compared to, say, in England,

00:06:03.583 --> 00:06:07.834
where the family breaks
after some time.

00:06:08.375 --> 00:06:11.834
At least here,
is much better.

00:06:27.125 --> 00:06:30.333
Shri Mataji, we in America
have a problem,

00:06:30.542 --> 00:06:33.250
that the seekers don't
stay in Sahaja Yoga.

00:06:34.125 --> 00:06:39.917
The seekers take their
realisation in America, and they don't stay in Sahaja Yoga.

00:06:40.125 --> 00:06:41.375
This is our problem.

00:06:42.792 --> 00:06:45.250
They don't stay.
Yes, Shri Mataji.

00:06:45.458 --> 00:06:48.917
Why?
I don't know Shri Mataji.

00:06:50.166 --> 00:06:52.208
It's not complete.

00:06:55.250 --> 00:06:59.125
If they have a complete
realisation,

00:06:59.667 --> 00:07:01.917
they will
have to come.

00:07:03.709 --> 00:07:08.000
They are not complete.
Just half way.

00:07:12.458 --> 00:07:16.291
They drink? Yes, Shri Mataji.
- That's the point.

00:07:18.417 --> 00:07:21.709
After coming to Sahaja Yoga
you cannot drink

00:07:21.875 --> 00:07:22.792
Yes, Shri Mataji

00:07:22.999 --> 00:07:28.250
And that must be the reason
they don't want to come.

00:07:29.458 --> 00:07:33.917
But you give them bandhans.
And beat them with shoes.

00:07:38.125 --> 00:07:41.458
Who are those...
your mother, father?

00:07:41.834 --> 00:07:44.667
My mother, my father,
yes. My good friends

00:07:46.166 --> 00:07:50.125
- they take realisation but they
don't stay as Sahaja Yogis.

00:07:50.583 --> 00:07:53.166
Because they drink.
- Yes, Shri Mataji.

00:07:56.333 --> 00:07:58.000
See now

00:08:01.999 --> 00:08:07.375
all your countries have
indulged into drinking.

00:08:08.125 --> 00:08:13.250
All over Europe, you see,
and it's a little fight,

00:08:13.667 --> 00:08:16.500
because for them
drinking is their life.

00:08:18.333 --> 00:08:20.959
We have to give
them bandhans.

00:08:24.999 --> 00:08:28.709
If you give them bandhans,
all of you put together

00:08:29.583 --> 00:08:32.000
then they cannot
run away.

00:08:33.667 --> 00:08:35.875
Bandhan has
to be given.

00:08:36.333 --> 00:08:39.750
All of you should
give bandhan.

00:08:50.041 --> 00:08:53.041
That's how they have
worked out in India.

00:08:53.999 --> 00:08:59.208
And India is, you know, how
Sahaja Yoga is strong there.

00:08:59.875 --> 00:09:02.291
The reason is
if they find

00:09:02.667 --> 00:09:06.750
parents are not coming, or maybe children
are not coming or whatever it is,

00:09:07.542 --> 00:09:10.000
they all work it out

00:09:11.709 --> 00:09:14.000
by giving them
bandhans.

00:09:15.875 --> 00:09:21.875
But first thing, you should
regularly come to SahajaYoga.

00:09:23.750 --> 00:09:25.500
Regularly.

00:09:26.500 --> 00:09:28.542
It is not half way,

00:09:28.999 --> 00:09:32.333
like today you come and
then you don't come.

00:09:33.500 --> 00:09:35.291
That's not proper.

00:09:36.667 --> 00:09:39.041
That's - you
cannot progress.

00:09:42.333 --> 00:09:45.208
You have to come
to the programmes,

00:09:45.959 --> 00:09:48.166
all of you, regularly.

00:09:48.875 --> 00:09:50.875
Because you know,

00:09:51.959 --> 00:09:54.917
realisation is
not easy thing.

00:09:55.875 --> 00:09:57.959
Nobody had it
before.

00:09:58.667 --> 00:10:01.166
Now you have got it.

00:10:01.750 --> 00:10:05.250
So you have to maintain
it and keep it up.

00:10:05.917 --> 00:10:08.750
Once you start
developing that

00:10:10.375 --> 00:10:13.458
the female of
the house also changes.

00:10:14.625 --> 00:10:17.375
Greatest problem
of Europe is

00:10:18.500 --> 00:10:21.583
- real problem, that
they drink.

00:10:22.959 --> 00:10:25.500
Drinking is the
main problem.

00:10:26.208 --> 00:10:29.542
And that's why they don't want
to come to Sahaja Yoga.

00:10:30.250 --> 00:10:34.041
But they can give their
parents, but not Sahaja Yoga.

00:10:36.875 --> 00:10:39.041
This is the trouble
with them.

00:10:42.583 --> 00:10:48.125
Parents can be given up, in case they
do not take to Sahaja Yoga.

00:10:49.417 --> 00:10:51.875
You should show
you don't like it.

00:10:53.000 --> 00:10:55.583
Why don't they
want Sahaja Yoga

00:10:58.750 --> 00:11:02.375
Because they drink, Shri Mataji.
Ah? - Because they drink.

00:11:02.750 --> 00:11:07.333
Now this is the curse of
Europe, that they all drink.

00:11:08.333 --> 00:11:13.834
And drinking is something
very difficult.

00:11:14.041 --> 00:11:17.375
They can't give it up, poor
things, they are slaves.

00:11:18.166 --> 00:11:19.999
Slaves of drinking.

00:11:21.000 --> 00:11:25.166
So by your behaviour, and
by your affection,

00:11:26.834 --> 00:11:29.583
I'm sure you can
win them over.

00:11:30.542 --> 00:11:34.125
What's the use - people who
drink die so early?

00:11:34.583 --> 00:11:38.999
You must have heard that
they die very fast.

00:11:39.999 --> 00:11:44.417
But despite that they don't realise
that one should not drink.

00:11:44.792 --> 00:11:50.125
Because it has become an open
market now for people.

00:11:49.999 --> 00:11:53.542
This is the biggest
problem of Europe.

00:11:54.291 --> 00:11:59.041
But do you know it is
much worse in America.

00:12:02.959 --> 00:12:08.125
America's problem
is so funny

00:12:08.542 --> 00:12:12.583
that people who
do Sahaja Yoga

00:12:13.917 --> 00:12:16.375
cannot convince
their parents.

00:12:17.583 --> 00:12:20.959
And they think
they have freedom

00:12:21.500 --> 00:12:23.542
to do whatever
they like.

00:12:25.125 --> 00:12:30.333
And some of the Sahaja Yogis have lost
their parents at a very early age.

00:12:32.166 --> 00:12:33.875
Very early age.

00:12:34.792 --> 00:12:37.458
Also they have parents

00:12:38.458 --> 00:12:42.583
who had heart...
heart attacks.

00:12:43.999 --> 00:12:45.583
All kinds of attacks.

00:12:45.834 --> 00:12:49.667
Not only heart but any
other disease they get.

00:12:50.041 --> 00:12:52.250
It's very funny,

00:12:53.458 --> 00:12:58.875
which they don't understand how
important it is to get realisation.

00:13:00.959 --> 00:13:03.458
So you should try
to talk to them,

00:13:03.999 --> 00:13:06.667
that "what is the aim
of your life."

00:13:07.959 --> 00:13:12.375
You must ask them: "What
is the aim of your life?

00:13:13.000 --> 00:13:18.583
You want to die or you
want to live?" - First question.

00:13:19.625 --> 00:13:22.375
If they say they want
to die, let them die.

00:13:22.709 --> 00:13:28.417
You should say: "Should we supply with
some wines for you when you die?"

00:13:29.458 --> 00:13:31.208
Make fun of it.

00:13:33.792 --> 00:13:35.542
Make a fun.

00:13:36.375 --> 00:13:40.542
So they will realise  that they
are stupid, who are drinking,

00:13:40.999 --> 00:13:43.000
and they are slaves.

00:13:43.709 --> 00:13:45.834
Slaves of drinking.

00:13:47.333 --> 00:13:51.125
They are not drinking because
they are free people.

00:13:53.000 --> 00:13:56.125
Because they
drink, they die.

00:13:56.999 --> 00:13:58.959
And die very fast.

00:14:00.000 --> 00:14:03.834
The complication of the
societies is so much.

00:14:05.125 --> 00:14:10.417
That I have seen people who were
rich, who had nice children,

00:14:10.917 --> 00:14:14.542
but they have lost
their parenthood.

00:14:15.291 --> 00:14:20.291
They have lost the children, and
they have no money also. They are on the street.

00:14:24.542 --> 00:14:29.041
Drinking is the best way
to waste all your money.

00:14:32.458 --> 00:14:35.000
They think then when
you say "don't drink",

00:14:35.208 --> 00:14:38.959
you are interested in
their money, maybe.

00:14:39.458 --> 00:14:44.125
God knows what they think because I don't
understand the psychology of people

00:14:44.291 --> 00:14:46.250
who drink.

00:14:47.166 --> 00:14:49.709
There are some
bhoots I think

00:14:49.999 --> 00:14:52.583
who give them
ideas like this.

00:14:53.166 --> 00:14:55.750
And they cannot
give up drinking.

00:14:57.375 --> 00:14:58.999
Very wrong.

00:15:00.834 --> 00:15:03.750
Where - in what book,

00:15:04.834 --> 00:15:07.875
I mean like Bible or
any book is said,

00:15:08.458 --> 00:15:10.583
that drinking is good?

00:15:12.834 --> 00:15:14.750
Did Christ drink?

00:15:15.917 --> 00:15:19.500
They will follow
Christianity.

00:15:22.000 --> 00:15:24.208
they will follow
Christianity.

00:15:25.166 --> 00:15:27.667
and not follow Christ.

00:15:28.875 --> 00:15:30.500
It's like that.

00:15:31.375 --> 00:15:35.417
Christ never drank. His
parents didn't drink.

00:15:35.834 --> 00:15:39.667
Now what makes them think
that they have a right to drink?

00:15:43.917 --> 00:15:46.166
Specially for Christians.

00:15:46.750 --> 00:15:51.417
Stupid they are if they think
that drinking is their right.

00:15:53.291 --> 00:15:57.000
And then they have
problems with drinking.

00:15:58.208 --> 00:16:01.667
Perhaps you know what
problems there are.

00:16:02.417 --> 00:16:06.667
You can find out what happens
when people are drunk.

00:16:07.125 --> 00:16:10.667
What happens to them,
where do they go,

00:16:11.583 --> 00:16:13.750
what is their position.

00:16:16.542 --> 00:16:18.917
You can find out
their friends,

00:16:19.333 --> 00:16:24.333
where are they, what they are
doing, how are they living.

00:16:25.834 --> 00:16:31.125
You'll be amazed, that they are
already on their way out.

00:16:35.041 --> 00:16:39.291
If you show your wisdom to
them, with assertion,

00:16:41.792 --> 00:16:44.125
they will be
coming around.

00:16:44.583 --> 00:16:49.000
You have to tell them.There's nothing
to feel shy about it.

00:16:51.291 --> 00:16:54.750
You have to tell them what
happens with drinking.

00:16:55.583 --> 00:16:58.041
What is so great
about it?

00:17:01.500 --> 00:17:05.917
Europe problem
is drinking - first.

00:17:06.917 --> 00:17:11.041
The second problem
is parenthood.

00:17:12.333 --> 00:17:16.458
Parents don't understand the
responsibility of their children,

00:17:18.250 --> 00:17:22.709
that all their lives they are going
to be children of yours.

00:17:23.792 --> 00:17:26.125
And you have to
look after them.

00:17:26.500 --> 00:17:29.542
There is no way
of getting it out.

00:17:30.999 --> 00:17:34.000
First of all why should
you have children?

00:17:34.542 --> 00:17:40.166
And if you have children, you have
to jolly well look after them.

00:17:41.375 --> 00:17:46.041
But I have seen that in Europe
people are really stupid.

00:17:48.041 --> 00:17:50.917
They don't understand
this simple fact,

00:17:51.999 --> 00:17:55.750
that if we cannot look
after ourselves,

00:17:56.000 --> 00:17:58.625
who will look after
our children?

00:18:01.291 --> 00:18:03.458
Very irresponsible.

00:18:04.417 --> 00:18:09.166
Also the society is such, that
in the society also,

00:18:09.709 --> 00:18:14.250
they just believe in drinking.
All of them.

00:18:17.125 --> 00:18:20.375
Indians who do
not drink in India,

00:18:20.999 --> 00:18:23.333
- here they come
and drink.

00:18:25.125 --> 00:18:27.041
When they come here

00:18:27.250 --> 00:18:31.709
then they think it is something
ideal, and they drink.

00:18:32.875 --> 00:18:36.375
I have known many like
that who came abroad

00:18:36.667 --> 00:18:38.959
and started drinking.

00:18:40.333 --> 00:18:42.917
So this is the big problem.

00:18:43.709 --> 00:18:47.875
You should openly talk
about it, to everyone

00:18:49.000 --> 00:18:51.834
That what is drinking
is stupidity

00:18:52.333 --> 00:18:57.917
- to become stupid,
by paying for it.

00:18:59.250 --> 00:19:04.500
Huh! You have to pay, and
you have to become mad.

00:19:05.750 --> 00:19:07.333
Just imagine.

00:19:07.875 --> 00:19:12.999
If you make fun of it, and if
you can tell them the truth

00:19:13.750 --> 00:19:19.250
I am sure they are all with the
intelligence, they will understand.

00:19:19.417 --> 00:19:22.291
But you should all
the time tell them.

00:19:27.959 --> 00:19:30.667
The third problem is
that here it is

00:19:30.959 --> 00:19:36.000
till you are an adult
you are away and free.

00:19:38.250 --> 00:19:40.375
But I can't understand

00:19:40.709 --> 00:19:44.792
- you are born
from your parents

00:19:45.542 --> 00:19:48.166
and how do you become
free after eighteen years

00:19:48.709 --> 00:19:52.208
or whatever age it is.

00:19:52.834 --> 00:19:54.458
How can that be?

00:19:57.250 --> 00:20:00.875
It's like a tree
producing fruits

00:20:01.208 --> 00:20:04.375
and the people take away
their fruits and eat it.

00:20:05.041 --> 00:20:09.542
We are not trees. We
are human beings

00:20:10.750 --> 00:20:13.250
We can't behave like trees

00:20:14.542 --> 00:20:16.999
which do not show
any interest

00:20:17.542 --> 00:20:20.375
in their children
after

00:20:20.917 --> 00:20:24.875
certain cutting
has happened.

00:20:27.250 --> 00:20:29.375
But it's very
surprising.

00:20:29.792 --> 00:20:34.500
See, for us Indians it's
absolutely surprising

00:20:34.959 --> 00:20:38.041
that they can forget about
their own children?

00:20:38.834 --> 00:20:40.500
How can
they do it?

00:20:42.291 --> 00:20:45.709
You have got writers who
have written stories

00:20:46.166 --> 00:20:48.875
and they have written
so many things here,

00:20:49.375 --> 00:20:52.959
that how can parents
be stupid like that?

00:20:54.875 --> 00:20:56.250
Whatever may be

00:20:56.583 --> 00:20:59.041
- whatever may be
your father or mother

00:20:59.333 --> 00:21:02.542
- they may be poor or
rich, whatever it is

00:21:02.750 --> 00:21:05.458
- they are
your parents!

00:21:06.041 --> 00:21:09.291
And parents are there
to look after you.

00:21:10.417 --> 00:21:15.583
The stupid thing is that they make
the child look after themselves

00:21:17.000 --> 00:21:21.458
When he is eighteen years
of old, he earns of his own

00:21:21.834 --> 00:21:24.500
and the parents:
"Alright, go ahead."

00:21:25.792 --> 00:21:28.542
They want to shirk all
the responsibility.

00:21:29.542 --> 00:21:31.500
Never heard of
such a thing.

00:21:31.709 --> 00:21:35.458
This is a very
recent fashion

00:21:40.291 --> 00:21:45.250
When Abraham Lincoln was
there, did it happen like that?

00:21:52.709 --> 00:21:55.291
Did it happen
with Christ

00:21:56.583 --> 00:22:02.333
that Mother gave him up and said:"Alright,
go ahead and get yourself crucified!"

00:22:07.000 --> 00:22:10.125
How can parents
behave like this?

00:22:10.959 --> 00:22:13.000
They have no heart?

00:22:15.375 --> 00:22:18.542
That they have no love
for their own children?

00:22:22.041 --> 00:22:24.250
India may not
be that rich,

00:22:24.458 --> 00:22:28.750
but people are loving
their children

00:22:35.041 --> 00:22:39.291
Children also here do
not listen to their parents,

00:22:40.166 --> 00:22:42.583
because parents don't
look after them.

00:22:43.583 --> 00:22:47.709
Can you imagine
a society

00:22:48.417 --> 00:22:51.166
religion, or whatever
you may call

00:22:51.750 --> 00:22:55.834
